metadata.name: Women of Mystery: Writer's Room Pass #1
metadata.description: Women of Mystery (WoM) is a storytelling collective open to everyone, where creators shape stories that will become the next generation of Hollywood IP. A WoM Writers Room access pass will unlock opportunities to learn from top Hollywood professionals, build IP using our decentralized story development platform and earn equity in the IP via your contributions. Visit www.womenofmystery.xyz and join Women of Mystery!
